data.name: ZentityAboutZentitySummary
data.value: Zentity aims to provide the necessary building blocks, tools, and services for developers who are tasked with creating and maintaining an organization’s repository ecosystem. Furthermore, it provides an easy-to-install and maintain experience for those who want to quickly set up a research output repository for their project, team, or organization. The platform is based on Microsoft’s technologies (SQL Server 2008 and .NET Framework version 3.5 SP1) hence taking advantage of their robustness, their quality support infrastructure, and the plethora of developer-focused documentation.

data.name: ZentityServiceAtomPubDescription
data.value: Zentity supports the AtomPub (Atom Publishing Protocol) for deposit scenarios. AtomPub service accepts GET, POST, PUT, DELETE requests for documents of any type. AtomPub service supports 22 collections that can be used to deposit resources of different resource types.

data.name: ZentityServiceOaiOreDescription
data.value: Zentity provides an OAI – ORE Service that supports Resource Map Implementation in RDF/XML. The service provides Resource Maps which are network accessible resources that encapsulate a set of RDF statements.

data.name: ZentityServiceOaiPmhDescription
data.value: User can make the metadata stored in Zentity searchable by common search engines. Common search engines support metadata harvesting through the OAI – PMH specification.

data.name: ZentityServiceSummary
data.value: Browse the extensive help on repository usage. This contains general learning material along with developer oriented help files and samples.

data.name: ZentityServiceSwordDescription
data.value: Zentity supports the SWORD APP Profile 1.2 – Level 0 for interoperable and bulk deposit between repository platforms. The SWORD service accepts GET, POST, PUT and DELETE requests for a document of any type.

data.name: ZentityServiceSyndicationDescription
data.value: Zentity provides both RSS and Atom syndication support for the resources in the database.
